headline: Shaping Tomorrow's Omnichannel Leaders with Cornell
summary: The way we shop for groceries has fundamentally changed, so how can professionals develop the skills needed to navigate this transformation? Kellanova Sales Learning & Development leader, Tomissa Smittendorf, shares more about this and Cornell University's Omnichannel Leadership Program in Kellanova's latest News Story.
